    <!-- Walkthrough / Tutorial -->
    <string name="walkthrough_title_1">1. Zoom</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_1">Use the slider to zoom the image. Digital zoom automatically kicks in beyond the hardware limit. Image stabilization reduces hand shake.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_2">2. Filters &amp; Sharpening</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_2">On the Filters and Adjustment tabs, you can improve text readability with accessibility color filters, contrast, and sharpening.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_3">3. Freeze &amp; Save</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_3">Use the large center button to freeze the image for comfortable reading. You can save or share the enhanced image with others.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_4">4. Text Reader &#38; Read Aloud</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_4">On frozen images, use the OCR button to recognize text, or the QR button to scan QR codes and barcodes.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_rotate_flip">5. Rotate &#38; Mirror Image</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_rotate_flip">On frozen images, use the Rotate button to turn the image by 90° increments, and the Flip button to mirror it horizontally for maximum readability.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_5">6. Focus &#38; Camera Modes</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_5">Use manual focus for sharp images. Successful focus is confirmed with haptic vibration. Turn on HDR or Night Boost mode in Settings!</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_6">7. Main Action Icons</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_6">Flash: For low light conditions.\nFreeze: Stop the live camera view for easy reading.\nRotate: Rotate frozen image by 90° steps.\nFlip: Mirror frozen image horizontally.\nSave: Save the enhanced image to your gallery.\nShare: Send the image directly to other apps.\nText Reader (OCR): Recognize and read aloud text.\nQR/Barcode: Scan QR codes and barcodes offline.</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_7">8. Sliders &#38; Adjustments</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_7">Zoom: Smooth logarithmic zoom.\nBrightness / Exposure: Brighten the image (tap value to reset to 0).\nContrast: Increase text contrast (tap value to reset to 1.0).\nSharpen: Sharpen text outline on frozen image (tap value to reset to 0.0).</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_title_8">9. Focus &#38; Settings</string>
    <string name="walkthrough_body_8">Auto Focus: Continuous auto focus.\nManual Focus Slider: Adjust focus manually (tap value to reset to Auto).\nTheme Dots: Customize the app\'s color theme.\nLanguage (flag): Switch between Hungarian and English.\nRate: Rate the app on the Play Store.</string>
